<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbc214174-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s2372"><num value="2372">§ 2372.</num><heading> Date of transfer of utilities</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Transfers of utilities shall be made as soon as possible, but in any event, not later than five years after <date date="1955-08-04">August 4, 1955</date>, in the case of Oak Ridge and Richland, or, in the case of Los Alamos, not later than <date date="1998-06-30">June 30, 1998</date>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbc214175-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/act/1955-08-04/ch543">Aug. 4, 1955, ch. 543</ref>, ch. 7, § 72, <ref href="/us/stat/69/480">69 Stat. 480</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/87/719/s20">Pub. L. 87–719, § 20</ref>, <date date="1962-09-28">Sept. 28, 1962</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/76/666">76 Stat. 666</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/104/106/dC/tXXXI/s3161/a">Pub. L. 104–106, div. C, title XXXI, § 3161(a)</ref>, <date date="1996-02-10">Feb. 10, 1996</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/110/627">110 Stat. 627</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idbc214176-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idbc214177-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="idbc214178-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1996—<ref href="/us/pl/104/106">Pub. L. 104–106</ref> substituted “not later than <date date="1998-06-30">June 30, 1998</date>” for “not later than five years after the date it is included within this chapter”.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1962—<ref href="/us/pl/87/719">Pub. L. 87–719</ref> inserted “in the case of Oak Ridge and Richland, or, in the case of Los Alamos, not later than five years after the date it is included within this chapter” after “<date date="1955-08-04">August 4, 1955</date>,”.</p>
</note>
</notes>
